feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 30, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kcm1665703231157.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kcm1665703231157.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kcm1665703231157.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kcm1665703231157\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$LIST_BOX\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the video attributes for a list box in character mode.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__topic_d141125e1_d141126e1_d141127e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__p_d141128e1_d141129e1_d141130e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LIST_BOX</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Selected</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Cleared</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__section_wgf_k3z_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222512e72\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__table_d16826e1_d16827e1_d16828e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">,INV</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__section_gjk_k3z_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222512e119\"> Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__p_d142763e1_d142764e1_d142765e1\">Each argument specifies one or more video attribute\n        codes. For more information, see the \"Video Attributes\" topic.. To define more than one\n        video attribute for each argument, separate them with commas and enclose them in\n        parentheses.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__section_kzn_k3z_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1222512e128\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__p_d141143e1_d141144e1_d141145e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LIST_BOX</span> is effective only when\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">$GUI=$CHR</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__p_d141146e1_d141147e1_d141148e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LIST_BOX</span> determines the video\n        attributes for the items in a list box in character mode. The video attributes defined by\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">Selected</var> are applied to the selected item, while the remaining items\n        appear as defined by <var class=\"keyword varname\">Cleared</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__p_d141149e1_d141150e1_d141151e1\">The default setting for a list box in character mode\n        is:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__pre_zzr_43z_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$LIST_BOX = ,INV</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__section_f1x_k3z_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle exampletitle\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__p_d141152e1_d141153e1_d141154e1\"> Example: $LIST_BOX </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__p_d141155e1_d141156e1_d141157e1\">To make the selected item in a list box appear with\n        blinking purple letters on a white background (40 + 7), while unselected items appear as\n        white letters on a purple background (56 + 5), use the following assignment:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kcm1665703231157__pre_h22_q3z_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$LIST_BOX = (BLI,COL=47), COL=61</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsj1665702873847.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Video Attributes</a><p>Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rez1688451198680.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ulistbox (ListBox )</a><p>The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529153\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529153\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$LIST_BOX Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 30, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $LIST_BOX Set the video attributes for a list box in character mode. $LIST_BOX { = } { Selected } , { Cleared } Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: ,INV Arguments Each argument specifies one or more video attribute codes. For more information, see the \"Video Attributes\" topic.. To define more than one video attribute for each argument, separate them with commas and enclose them in parentheses. Description $LIST_BOX is effective only when $GUI=$CHR . $LIST_BOX determines the video attributes for the items in a list box in character mode. The video attributes defined by Selected are applied to the selected item, while the remaining items appear as defined by Cleared . The default setting for a list box in character mode is: $LIST_BOX = ,INV Copy Example: $LIST_BOX To make the selected item in a list box appear with blinking purple letters on a white background (40 + 7), while unselected items appear as white letters on a purple background (56 + 5), use the following assignment: $LIST_BOX = (BLI,COL=47), COL=61 Copy Related Links Video Attributes Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences. ulistbox (ListBox ) The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}